spec_data.Name: perl-Authen-CAS-Client
spec_data.Description:
The Authen::CAS::Client module provides a simple interface for
authenticating users using JA-SIG's CAS protocol. Both CAS v1.0 and v2.0
are supported.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 07:16:40 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Interface for authentication via JA-SIG's Central Authentication Service
